Package de.lmu.dbs.jfeaturelib.features.lire Description

The lire package contain slightly modified feature classes from LIRE (Lucene Image REtrieval).

The modifications should not regard the processing code but only to obtain the results of the extraction process.

The classes of this package should NOT be used directly except from the according classes in the de.lmu.dbs.jfeaturelib.features package.
